      If something here caused you to pause,<br>
      if questions arose that had not arisen before —<br>
      that is not accidental.
    </p>

    <p>
      Learning can continue.<br>
      Slowly. Thoughtfully.<br>
      With responsibility.
    </p>

    <div class="emphasis">
      The learning is shared in spirit.<br>
      The path is always personal.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

